title: Uncle Mike's Superlicious BBQ
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Southern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. BBQ restaurant. Menu is mostly meat stuff but includes veg choices like: a tofu sandwich with portobello mushroom, onions, and bell peppers on a grilled roll with BBQ aioli sauce; a sandwich with marinated eggplant, onions, and cucumbers grilled with smoked button mushroom and topped with fresh tomatoes on a grilled roll with BBQ aioli sauce; a BBQ portobello cutlet entree over rice; and various sides.
